AUTHORS OF PAIN VS NEW DAY GOES TO NO CONTEST

ODYSSEY JONES HAS ARRIVED TO MONDAY NIGHT RAW OVER A YEAR AFTER BEING DRAFTED TO THE BRAND

JONES TAKES OUT KARRION KROSS AND THE AUTHORS OF PAIN ALL ON HIS OWN AND APPEARS TO JOIN THE NEW DAY

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f1141f32-249a-4314-bfaa-a6a8b71e6bbe/Screenshot_20240805_184007.jpg)

Kofi Kingston introduces Odyssey Jones to Xavier Woods. Woods feels uncomfortable because he didn't know they even knew each other.

Before he can say something about it, Alpha Academy comes in because TOZAWA wants to show Xavier Woods his new dance.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ff8194f2-7345-458b-9d11-991154ab6d0f/Screenshot_20240805_184032.jpg)

