*   ## **_A TOWN DOWN UNDER_** _DEF. AWESOME TRUTH_
    

Comic relief match that saw the Miz and R-Truth working like the Rock N Roll Express for a bit.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b5b5b6bf-80e1-4b1b-934c-025f546ecf90/Screenshot_20240805_185936.jpg)

Bron Breakker says nobody will take his name off of the Intercontinental Championship

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/afb47c7f-8958-406a-9751-ba981cfbdbde/Screenshot_20240805_190318.jpg)

*   ## **_DAMIEN PRIEST DEF. JD MCDONOUGH_** _BY DQ_
    

Damien Priest and JD McDonough actually have a pretty damn good match until the rest of Judgement Day gets involved.

They're beating on Damien Priest and he's able to fight off Carlito, JD and Balor and Liv and Dom are jumping Priest when Rhea finally arrives.

Rhea runs out and gets her hands on Liv for a minute until Dom steals Liv away. Rhea and Priest take the left behind JD McDonough and destroy him in the ring.

Incredible crowd. Incredible segment.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/64db8322-ce30-43b7-acbe-1721f6493b08/Screenshot_20240805_191542.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f6af3a2b-1621-47e6-84f0-cfae3ff9c524/Screenshot_20240805_191931.jpg)

Sonya DeVille and her group take out Dakota Kai so that there won't be a match tonight. But Iyo Sky takes Dakota’s place in the match.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a84d38bc-65aa-4753-ab65-ca4d5c59aad9/Screenshot_20240805_192948.jpg)

*   ## **_IYO SKY DEF. SONYA DEVILLE_**
    

Damage CTRL and the rest of Sonya’s group brawl at ringside and this gives Iyo an opening to defeat Sonya.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a59a6f22-eef4-4f8c-a93b-fe7a9554f789/Screenshot_20240805_193815.jpg)

CHAD GABLE AND THE CREED BROS ARE OFFICIALLY KNOWN AS..... AMERICAN MADE.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5fc469b4-477e-4c36-82f7-9ad4847c8b53/Screenshot_20240805_194841.jpg)

*   ## **_WYATT SICKS DEF. AMERICAN MADE_**
    

Wyatt Sick6 make their entrance to Bray Wyatt’s full theme song. They had been teasing it with the first note since their debut.

Joe Gacy, Dexter Lumis and Erik Rowan wrestle as a trios while Uncle Howdy and Nikki Cross watch from outside.

Great showing from both teams.